le.text\\n                    }\\n                }\\n            }\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_10\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '1,240p' settings.gradle\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_10\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '1,240p' settings.gradle\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"/*\\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\\n *\\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\\n */\\npluginManagement {\\n    includeBuild(\\\"tests/tck-build-logic\\\")\\n    repositories {\\n        mavenLocal()\\n        gradlePluginPortal()\\n    }\\n}\\n\\nrootProject.name = \\\"reachability-metadata\\\"\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_11\",\"type\":\"agent_message\",\"text\":\"There is an existing root task named `generateChangedMetadataTestMatrix`, which looks like the likely replacement. I’m confirming whether the failing gate still invokes the older `generateChangedTestedVersionsMatrix` name and whether an alias is enough.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_12\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc \\\"rg -n \\\\\\\"generateChangedMetadataTestMatrix\\\\\\\" build.gradle tests/tck-build-logic -g '\\\"'!build/**'\\\"'\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_12\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc \\\"rg -n \\\\\\\"generateChangedMetadataTestMatrix\\\\\\\" build.gradle tests/tck-build-logic -g '\\\"'!build/**'\\\"'\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/